Kathleen Kirkham https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Kathleen_Kirkham 0 Kathleen Kirkham (April 15, 1895 – November 7, 1961) was a silent film actress from Menominee, Michigan. Her mother, Mrs. L.B. Kirkham, resided at 1135 Windsor Boulevard in Los Angeles, California. She was a stage actress prior to marriage.
